orneo Post]]|accessdate=25 October 2018|url=http://www.theborneopost.com/2013/09/14/muhyiddin-heads-list-of-tyt-birthday-award-recipients/|title=Muhyiddin heads list of TYT birthday award recipients|date=14 September 2013}}</ref>\n** [[File:MY-SAR Order of the Star of the Hornbill (Bintang Kenyalang) - 1. Knight Grand Commander (DP).svg|50px]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak#Datuk Patinggi Bintang Kenyalang (D.P.)|Order of the Star of Hornbill Sarawak]] (DP) - '''Datuk Patinggi''' (2016)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=12 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2016/09/09/zahid-heads-list-of-115-sarawak-state-award-recipients/|work=[[Bernama]]|title=Zahid heads list of 115 Sarawak state award recipients|date=9 September 2016}}</ref>\n\n==See also==\n*[[Bagan Datok (federal constituency)]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Ahmad Zahid Hamidi}}\n* {{url|https://ahmadzahidhamidi.wordpress.com/|Official blog}} \n* {{facebook|zahidhamidi.fanpage}}\n* {{pom|3598}}\n\n{{S-start}}\n{{S-off}}\n|-\n{{S-bef|before=[[Wan Azizah Wan Ismail]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Leader of the Opposition (Malaysia)|Leader of the Opposition]]|years= 2018-2019}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Ismail Sabri Yaakob]]}}\n{{S-bef|before=[[Muhyiddin Yassin]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Deputy Prime Minister of Malaysia]]|years= 2015\u20132018}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Wan Azizah Wan Ismail]]}}\n{{S-end}}\n\n{{Deputy Prime Ministers of Malaysia}}\n{{Perak-FedRep}}\n{{Third Abdullah cabinet}} \n{{First Najib cabinet}} \n{{Second Najib cabinet}}\n{{Portal bar|Malaysia|Biography|Politics}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Zahid Hamidi, Ahmad}}\n[[Category:1953 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Perak]]\n[[Category:Malaysian people of Javanese descent]]\n[[Category:Malaysian people of Malay descent]]\n[[Category:Malaysian Muslims]]\n[[Category:Leaders of politic