ays National Organisation|UMNO]])\n| rowspan=3 align=\"right\"|18,909\n| rowspan=3|51.37%\n|-\n|{{Party shading/Keadilan}} |\n|Pakhrurrazi Arshad ([[People's Justice Party (Malaysia)|PKR]])\n|align=\"right\" |13,836\n|37.59%\n| rowspan=3|37,620\n| rowspan=3|5,073\n| rowspan=3|79.89%\n|-\n|{{Party shading/PAS}} |\n|Ata Abdul Muneim Hasan Adli ([[Pan-Malaysian Islamic Party|PAS]])\n|align=\"right\" |4,061\n|11.03%\n|-\n|}\n\n== Honours ==\n* {{Flag|Kelantan}} :\n** [[File:MY-KEL Order of the Crown of Kelantan - Star of Muhammad.svg|50px]] Knight Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Kelantan|Order of the Crown of Kelantan]] (DPMK) - '''Dato'''' (2005)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=25 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2005/04/02/sultan-of-kelantan-birthday-honours-list/|title=Sultan of Kelantan birthday honours list|date=2 April 2005}}</ref>\n** [[File:My-KEL Order of the Life of the Crown of Kelantan 2006.svg|50px]] Knight Grand Commander of the [[Orders, decorations, and medals of Kelantan|Order of the Life of the Crown of Kelantan]] (SJMK) - '''Dato'''' (2009)<ref name=\":1\" /><ref>{{cite web|publisher=[[The Star (Malaysia)|The Star]]|accessdate=25 October 2018|url=https://www.thestar.com.my/news/nation/2009/03/31/constitution-must-be-respected-says-kelantan-sultan/|work=[[Bernama]]|title=Constitution must be respected, says Kelantan Sultan|date=31 March 2009}}</ref>\n* {{Flag|Malacca}} :\n** [[File:MY-MAL Exalted Order of Malacca.svg|50px]] Companion Class I of the [[List of post-nominal letters (Malacca)|Exalted Order of Malacca]] (DMSM) - '''Datuk''' (1993)<ref name=\":1\">{{cite web|url=http://www.istiadat.gov.my/index.php/component/semakanlantikanskp/|title=SEMAKAN PENERIMA DARJAH KEBESARAN, BINTANG DAN PINGAT|publisher=[[Prime Minister's Department (Malaysia)]]|accessdate=25 October 2018}}</ref>\n** [[File:MY-MAL Exalted Order of Malacca.svg|50px]] Knight Grand Com